#: ../../source/background.rst:56
msgid "Problem Formulation"
msgstr "问题定义"

#: ../../source/background.rst:58
msgid ""
"In the context of online portfolio selection, we analyze a financial "
"market consisting :math:`m` assets observed during a specified time "
"horizon comprising :math:`n` discrete trading periods (the term "
"\"periods\" is defined flexibly). At the end of the :math:`t`-th trading "
"period, we use a :math:`m`-dimensional non-negative price relatives "
"vector :math:`\\mathbf{x}_t=(x_{t,1},\\ldots,x_{t,m}) \\in "
"\\mathbb{R}_{+}^{m}` to represent the performance of the :math:`m` "
"assets, where each element :math:`x_{t,i}` equals the close price of "
"asset :math:`i` on the :math:`t`-th trading period divided by the close "
"price of asset :math:`i` on the :math:`(t-1)`-th trading period, i.e., "
":math:`x_{t,i}={C_{t,i}}/{C_{t-1,i}}`."
msgstr ""
"在在线投资组合选择的背景下，我们分析了一个由 :math:`m` 种资产组成的金融市场，这些资产在由 :math:`n` 个离散交易期 (术语 "
"\"周期\"的定义是灵活的) 组成的特定时间段内进行观察。在第 :math:`t` 个交易期结束时，"
"我们使用一个 :math:`m` 维的非负相对价格向量 :math:`\\mathbf{x}_t=(x_{t,1},\\ldots,x_{t,m}) \\in \\mathbb{R}_{+}^{m}` "
"来表示 :math:`m` 个资产的表现，其中元素 :math:`x_{t,i}` 等于第 :math:`t` 个交易期资产 :math:`i` "
"的收盘价除以第 :math:`(t-1)` 个交易期资产 :math:`i` 的收盘价，即 :math:`x_{t,i}={C_{t,i}}/{C_{t-1,i}}`。"

#: ../../source/background.rst:67
msgid ""
"Before the start of the :math:`t`-th trading period, using past "
"historical information, we can construct a portfolio vector "
":math:`\\mathbf{b}_t=(b_{t,1},\\ldots,b_{t,m}) \\in \\mathbb{R}^m` to "
"allocate our wealth among :math:`m` assets. Each element :math:`b_{t,i}` "
"represents the proportion of wealth invested in asset :math:`i` at the "
"beginning of the :math:`t`-th trading period. A portfolio clearly needs "
"to satisfy the simplex constraint :math:`\\mathbf{b}_t \\in \\Delta_m`, "
"where :math:`b_{t,i} \\ge 0` and "
":math:`\\sum\\nolimits_{i=1}^{m}{{{b}_{t,i}}}=1`. This constraint "
"indicates the portfolio is fully self-financing without leverage or "
"shorting."
msgstr ""
"在第 :math:`t` 个交易期开始之前，利用过去的历史信息，"
"我们可以构建一个投资组合向量 :math:`\\mathbf{b}_t=(b_{t,1},\\ldots,b_{t,m}) \\in \\mathbb{R}^m` "
"以在 :math:`m` 个资产中分配我们的财富。每个元素 :math:`b_{t,i}` "
"代表在第 :math:`t` 个交易期开始时，投资于资产 :math:`i` 的财富比例。投资组合显然需要"
"满足简单约束：:math:`\\mathbf{b}_t \\in \\Delta_m`，其中其中：:math:`b_{t,i} \\ge 0` 且 "
":math:`\\sum\\nolimits_{i=1}^{m}{{{b}_{t,i}}}=1`。 这个约束表明投资组合是完全自融资的，不允许杠杆或做空。"

#: ../../source/background.rst:75
msgid ""
"Therefore, at the end of the :math:`t`-th trading period, the daily "
"return of the portfolio is defined as :math:`\\mathbf{b}_{t}^{\\top} "
"\\mathbf{x}_t = \\sum\\nolimits_{i=1}^{m} b_{t,i}x_{t,i}`. Based on this,"
" the final wealth achieved at the end of the :math:`n`-th trading period "
"is:"
msgstr ""
"因此，在第 :math:`t` 个交易期结束时，投资组合的每日回报定义为 :math:`\\mathbf{b}_{t}^{\\top}  "
"\\mathbf{x}_t = \\sum\\nolimits_{i=1}^{m} b_{t,i}x_{t,i}`。据此，"
"投资组合在第 :math:`n` 个交易期结束时实现的最终财富为："

